data.description: Discover the charm of this split-level gem nestled in a serene cul-de-sac within a peaceful neighborhood. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, the home welcomes you with high ceilings in the foyer, creating an inviting atmosphere. Enjoy the expansive front and back yards, ideal for outdoor activities, complemented by a spacious deck for relaxation. The full unfinished basement offers endless potential for customization. While minor cosmetic updates await your personal touch, this residence promises a tranquil haven with room to make it uniquely yours.
